{"tid":1270721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉國謙：有人藉不合作運動令社會不安","createTime":"2019-07-01T02:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T02:52:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7cdd9aea98b6bfac27731c3b389c1957b115e3","tid":1270721,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席七一回歸酒會致詞，提到近日的《逃犯條例》修訂爭議，表示會汲取教訓，確保施政更貼近民心民情。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員葉國謙表示，相信林鄭月娥已說了心底話，並已就修例事件道歉，批評有些人<span style=\"color: red;\">藉不合作運動造成社會不安</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於有訴求要求不檢控示威者，他認為本港是法治社會，加上昨日的「撐警」活動反映<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">很多市民</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持警方維護治安，<span style=\"color: red;\">不可能不追究犯罪者</span>。<br />\n<br />\nSource：信報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2178203/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2178203%2F&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=9d82721b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2178203/</a>"},{"pid":"a1f40efab7c4375ace89fe83fe3a77812e0bb2af","tid":1270721,"uid":4462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"有幾撚多市民？有無證據，無就咪撚鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港真係多啲呢啲柒頭先搞到今時今日咁樣"},{"pid":"feef9fe3cb57070bab82a50178d1efd96707a957","tid":1270721,"uid":9356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7cdd9aea98b6bfac27731c3b389c1957b115e3","tid":1270721,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席七一回歸酒會致詞，提到近日的《逃犯條例》修訂爭議，表示會汲取教訓，確保施政更貼近民心民情。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員葉國謙表示，相信林鄭月娥已說了心底話，並已就修例事件道歉，批評有些人<span style=\"color: red;\">藉不合作運動造成社會不安</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於有訴求要求不檢控示威者，他認為本港是法治社會，加上昨日的「撐警」活動反映<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">很多市民</span>